item.title: Join the Club
item.description: Anyone interested in developing software is welcome to attend a Programming Club meeting. We are meeting remotely on Discord all summer. Check the discord for the latest meeting time; likely Sundays at 5:00 pm. Last semester, we meet on Tuesdays at 11:00 am in Coover 115 on the PennWest campus, but we may be changing to an Eberly location for Fall of 2023. Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/9mkqjeEy (Link expires 5/21)
